{
  "design_notes": "A balanced and dynamic Medium chart designed to align with the electronic structure of the track. The chart transitions from a sparse and atmospheric intro into a steady, energetic stream of 8th notes and well-placed jumps during the main drops. Jumps are mapped specifically to high-amplitude snare and synth accents (using dual onsets at identical beats). The break section is mapped as a breather with holds and light footsteps, followed by a dramatic drop transition in the second half. Outro fades out smoothly using structured grid taps to keep the player engaged without causing fatigue.",
